page.title: 20CLASS SIX AT SPROATLEY
page.content: The Children in Class Six at Sproatley completed the Domesday Project during July,1985. The Children involved were all aged 10 and their names are, Joanna Parkinson Michael Napierski Donna Wood Vicki Strong Kirsty Cochran Katie Stead Philip Stannard Daniel Quest Hayley Rollinson Robert Leonard Peter Lomas Richard Gwilliam Darren Ruston Charlotte Sowerby Jane Gibson Robert Newton Christopher Whitton Paul Asquith Matthew Hopkin Caroline Freeman Jane Chittenden Angela Breen Faye Dickinson Ruth Evans Kerry Goforth Katy Lowe Nicola Hyam Zoe Pindar Stephen Platten Louise Todd Janice Wilcock Catherine Heckford Tracy Corderoy
